## Using Fuse ESB

### How does Fuse ESB differ from Apache ServiceMix

* Fuse ESB comes integrated with [Fuse Fabric](../fabric/index) for improved clustering, partitioning, discovery and load balancing.
* Fuse ESB comes integrated with [Fuse Bundle](../bundle/index) for simpler development and deployment of OSGi based applications.
